Sure, here are a few examples of sentences in Serbian that use the word "osnovi" in different forms and positions:

1. Učimo *osnove* matematike. (We're learning the *basics* of mathematics.)
2. *Osnovi* fizike su nam jako važni za ovaj projekt. (*The fundamentals* of physics are very important for this project.)
3. Treba da se pridržavaš *osnovnih* pravila ponašanja. (You need to follow *basic* rules of behavior.)
4. Naša firma se bavi *osnovnim* istraživanjima u oblasti medicine. (Our company is engaged in *fundamental* research in the field of medicine.)
5. *Osnova* našeg sporazuma je uzajamno poštovanje. (*The basis* of our agreement is mutual respect.)

I hope these examples help!